{"tid":1379613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN：香港警察使用美製催淚彈","createTime":"2019-07-28T21:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:24:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3272343b17c3d9a904d26594f03b7626696b21f7","tid":1379613,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dynaimage.cdn.cnn.com/cnn/digital-images/org/90379ff2-12be-4d67-b129-c2db111a9d11.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdynaimage.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnn%2Fdigital-images%2Forg%2F90379ff2-12be-4d67-b129-c2db111a9d11.jpeg&h=a0196aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dynaimage-cdn-cnn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/dynaimage.cdn.cnn.com/cnn/digital-images/w_900,h_1200/7897495f-8913-4c6e-8869-97d1ba364774.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdynaimage-cdn-cnn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fdynaimage.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnn%2Fdigital-images%2Fw_900%2Ch_1200%2F7897495f-8913-4c6e-8869-97d1ba364774.jpeg&h=76d8f87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）周日報道，港警周日晚用於驅散中上環示威者的催淚彈，當中包括由美國製造的。<br />\n<br />\nCNN記者從遺留地上催淚彈殼，發現催氣彈由美國賓夕凡尼亞州人群控制產品製造商「NonLethal Technologies」生產。<br />\n<br />\n另外，CNN記者又發現，警方用於驅散示威者的橡膠子彈，以大小和重量判斷，雖不足以致命，一旦被擊中卻也可造成相當痛楚。報道又指出，從社交網絡流傳的圖片所見，中彈記者和示威者胸部和手臂都呈現手掌大小的瘀痕。"},{"pid":"898fb0b65f77e3433e1c1fd7f30a398241a83008","tid":1379613,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:58:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190729/59873985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59873985&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=bcb2ba49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190729%2F59873985&h=31705192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190729/59873985</a>"},{"pid":"86c2a91d9d0eeb8940fee87430da62cec5f07031","tid":1379613,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:59:02.000Z","msg":"又收錢又外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8320585d9c016b72bf07d88950ae03851a6252bd","tid":1379613,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:02:22.000Z","msg":"外國勢力"},{"pid":"51c3e605c1d3a7c3116ec4ea15fecfb13839c4f1","tid":1379613,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fBqC4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fBqC4d.png&h=64249127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df282aee98437d583c80d0fba81c062ccd479fc4","tid":1379613,"uid":37396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:06:34.000Z","msg":"nonlethal 呢個名真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5822fc89c5441a5a93e8f04c3192ff6190c44575","tid":1379613,"uid":165442,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:07:10.000Z","msg":"外國勢力<br />\n推去藍絲谷 示威處發現美製武器<br />\n<br />\n等佢地推到夠noise<br />\n再比佢地知狗放"},{"pid":"ef0c69d6e146bad1298e6ac98554c0b5394b5e30","tid":1379613,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:52:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4a729c83417a8e332a4e3b9a1814f29a1c25b5b0","tid":1379613,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:52:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[八五三罷] 對8月5號罷工一事有感而發<br /